          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Hi there,\nI just want to express my thoughts about Rama Devi School. I’m happy that I selected Rama Devi for my little one’s education. Both- my kid and I are satisfied with the study pattern the school follows. They have great teaching staff that makes my child understand every concept clearly. The environment here is friendly, amenities are good, and they have many extra curriculum activities to help their students in grow better.\nThanks Rama Devi International School!",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
